1. *Oseća* se da će ovo biti jako korisno. (He feels that this will be very useful.)
2. On je *osećao* da je nešto pogrešno. (He felt that something was wrong.)
3. Moramo *osećati* zahvalnost za ono što imamo. (We must feel gratitude for what we have.)
4. Naše srca *osećaju* tugu. (Our hearts feel sadness.)
5. *Osećala* je da joj neko prati pogled. (She felt that someone was watching her.)
6. On je *osećao* da je preplavljen stresom. (He felt that he was overwhelmed with stress.)
7. *Osećaš* li toplinu sunca? (Do you feel the warmth of the sun?)